Properties.Caption: Просмотр реестра заключений на зачет доходов по ПД
Properties.Tag: Select [K_TD].[CTD] As [Тип документа], [Apps_Groups].[GroupName] As [Группа], Max([Apps_Groups].[GroupCaption]) As [Наименование группы], [DOC].[CDOC] As [Документ], [DOC].[DDOC] As [Дата реестра], [DOC_1].[CDOC] As [Заключение], [DOC_1].[DDOC] As [Дата документа], [DOC].[DU_R] As [Дата распорядителя], RTrim([K_D].[CDS]) As [Со статьи доходов], Max([K_D].[NS]) As [Наименование статьи дохода], RTrim([K_D_1].[CDS]) As [Статья доходов], Max([K_D_1].[NS]) As [Наименование статьи доходов], Sum([ZF_D_1].[SUMM]) As [Сумма] From ((((((((([DOC] With (NoLock) Inner Join [DOC_DOC] With (NoLock) On ([DOC].[DOCID]=[DOC_DOC].[DOCID] And [DOC].[K_TDID]=[DOC_DOC].[K_TDID])) Inner Join [DOC] As [DOC_1] With (NoLock) On ([DOC_DOC].[DOCID_PARENT]=[DOC_1].[DOCID] And [DOC_DOC].[K_TDID_PARENT]=[DOC_1].[K_TDID])) Left Join [ZF_D] With (NoLock) On ([DOC_1].[DOCID]=[ZF_D].[DOCID] And [DOC_1].[K_TDID]=[ZF_D].[K_TDID] And Sgn([ZF_D].[SUMM])=-1)) Left Join [K_D] With (NoLock) On ([ZF_D].[K_DID]=[K_D].[K_DID] And [ZF_D].[K_D_TYPE]=[K_D].[K_D_TYPE])) Left Join [ZF_D] As [ZF_D_1] With (NoLock) On ([DOC_1].[DOCID]=[ZF_D_1].[DOCID] And [DOC_1].[K_TDID]=[ZF_D_1].[K_TDID] And Sgn([ZF_D_1].[SUMM])<>-1)) Left Join [K_D] As [K_D_1] With (NoLock) On ([ZF_D_1].[K_DID]=[K_D_1].[K_DID] And [ZF_D_1].[K_D_TYPE]=[K_D_1].[K_D_TYPE])) Inner Join [K_TD] With (NoLock) On ([DOC].[K_TDID]=[K_TD].[K_TDID])) Inner Join [Apps_Groups] With (NoLock) On ([DOC].[Apps_GroupsID]=[Apps_Groups].[Apps_GroupsID])) Inner Join [K_UL] With (NoLock) On (Mid([DOC].[CDOC],1,10)=[K_UL].[CUL])) Where [DOC_DOC].[K_TDID]=635 And [DOC_DOC].[K_TDID_PARENT]=972 And [DOC].[K_BDID]=GetK_BDID() And |0 Group by [K_TD].[CTD], [Apps_Groups].[GroupName], [DOC].[CDOC], [DOC].[DDOC], [DOC_1].[CDOC], [DOC_1].[DDOC], [DOC].[DU_R], RTrim([K_D].[CDS]), RTrim([K_D_1].[CDS]) Order by |1
Properties.Name: Просмотр реестра заключений на зачет доходов по ПД
